    {
      "id": "18e4750c-f3ba-80dd-a258-e8794a46c8c7",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "MOOCs are becoming more and more prevalent in higher education. However, this proliferation follows the traditional educational paradigm in many regards. The paper shows tha BKT can be adapted to a course on edX. The experiment tests BKTs success on 3 distinct challenges: lack of knowledge component models, unpenalized multiple attempts for quizzes/tests and diverging learning pathways through the system.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "18e4750c-f3ba-80dd-a258-e8794a46c8c7",
        "parent": {
